Andre Blackman has been told he is surplus to requirements by Blackpool FC boss Lee Clark . 
  Blackman stole a jacket worth more than £1,000 from Harrods in Knightsbridge . 
  He was ordered to carry out 40 hours of unpaid work as part of a 12-month community order . 
  The 24-year-old said the offence was a ‘moment of madness’ Blackman told the judge he was trying to find a new club . 
 